  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Qualifications in COVID-19 support packages
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">The qualifications Education and Skills Funding Agency will fund to support economic recovery following the COVID-19 outbreak.</p>

